WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
CARIBBEAN SEA.
BAHAMAS TO JAMAICA.
DNC 14, DNC 16.
48 FOOT VESSEL FATAL ATTRACTION,
FOUR PERSONS ON BOARD, OVERDUE
GREAT INAGUA (21-03.4N 073-25.5W) TO
JAMAICA (17-59N 076-48W). VESSELS IN
VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP
LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
REPORTS TO RCC MIAMI, PHONE: 305 415 6800,
E-MAIL: RCCMIAMI@USCG.MIL.
